import React from 'react'
import {
	Grid,
	GridItem,
	Flex,
	Button,
	Heading,
	Box,
	Spacer,
	Input
} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { useState } from 'react'


const Container = () => {

	const [login, setLogin] = useState('');
	const [password, setPassword] = useState('');

	
	return (
		<Grid h='100px' 
		templateRows='repeat(2, 1fr)'
		templateColumns='repeat(3, 1fr)'
		>
			<GridItem rowSpan={1} colSpan={3} bg='tomato'>
				<Flex align='center'>
					<Box p='2'>
						<Heading size='md' mt='8px'>Placeholder App</Heading>
					</Box>
					<Spacer />
					<Box>
						<Button colorScheme='teal' mr='4' mt='1'>
							Sign Up
						</Button>
						<Button colorScheme='teal' mt='1'>Log in</Button>
					</Box>
				</Flex>
			</GridItem>
			<GridItem rowStart={2} colSpan={1}>
				<Input placeholder='login' onClick={(e) => setLogin(e.target.value)}/>
			</GridItem>
		</Grid>
	)
}

export default Container;
